/*
  AtomS3R IMU calibration wizard (Accel + Gyro + Mag) using imu_cal::* calibrators.

  UI goals:
    - Simple, short prompts
    - Auto flow (no button needed during poses; screen may be down)
    - Only show progress + what to do
    - Debug numbers go to Serial, not screen

  Start:
    - Tap screen (BtnA) on STATUS screen, OR Serial 'S'
  Erase:
    - Serial 'E' only

  REQUIREMENTS:
    - M5Unified
    - Preferences (ESP32 Arduino)
    - ArduinoEigenDense
    - CalibrateIMU_alt.h
*/

